set.name: Don DiMello's 'Disney's Wizard of Oz' is Staged in Pasadena
set.article: Don DiMello's 'Disney's Wizard of Oz' opened June 8 2012 (off-hours) at the Pasadena Fairytale Theatre. The show took several liberties with the original narrative and, during production, under the childcare of Cactus Tony, an unnamed 8-year-old boy was ripped apart by several lactating Rottweilers. The show failed to reach denouement.
